aVAnyway, so I'm proposing that an alternative primary education,
p107
aVwhatever alternative you want, is required where schools don't exist,
p108
aVwhere schools are not good enough, where teachers are not available
p109
aVor where teachers are not good enough, for whatever reason.
p110
aVIf you happen to live in a part of the world where none of this applies,
